name: Lemony Lemongrass Whipped Shea Butter 8oz
description:
Unrefined shea Butter,Coconut Oil,Meadowfoam seed Oil,Vitamin E,Castor Oil, Evening Primrose Oil, Beeswax, Tapioca Starch, Lemon essential Oil, Lemongrass Essential Oil 

Unrefined Shea Butter- it helps with various Skin Ailments Like ECZEMA,PSORIASIS and in some cases ROSACIA. Also it helps to RESTORE ELASTICITY to the skin, and what I LOVE is that it helps MINIMIZE STRETCH MARKS and SCARS and is GREAT for DRY CRACKING skin and RASHES 

Coconut Oil- Acne, varicose veins and signs of aging can all be treated with coconut oil. It’s a wonderful natural body lotion and will give your skin a healthy glow as well as REDUCE the appearance of STRETCH MARKS. 

Castor Oil- Castor oil’s ability to penetrate more deeply than any other essential plant oil make it an excellent way to keep skin looking youthful and fresh. It also has ricinoleic acid which works to inhibit many viruses and bacteria so its great for treating acne. 

Meadowfoam Seed Oil- MOISTURIZES the skin and gives a smooth texture to my formula. 

Vitamin E - Very MOISTURIZING and GREAT for minimizing STRETCH MARKS and SCARS 

Evening Primrose oil-  is high in gamma-linolenic acid (an essential fatty acid) making it an exceptional skin nourishing oil. The human body does not produce essential fatty acids such as linoleic and linolenic acids. It, therefore, is important to get these nutrients through diet and topical application. Essential fatty acids inhibit bacterial growth and allow our systems to defend against infection and inflammation. Organic Evening Primrose Oil is highly recommended for DRY SKIN problems such as ECZEMA and PSORIASIS. 

Beeswax- is Moisturizing and gives a nice smooth finish to your skin

Tapioca Starch- Helps with the smooth application and also makes it not so greasy  

Lemon Essential Oil- antiseptic and smells like a fresh lemon also is said to help with cellulite 

Lemongrass Essential Oil-  smells like a blend of lemon and grass. also is an astringent and helps treat acne and oily skin. Lemongrass acts as a good skin toner and also helps with aching muscles
